rComments: An incredible professor who makes a very hard course quite easy to understand. I ONLY studied off the notes he gave us, and paid attention in class. I didn't even open the textbook, and I did above the average in the class.
Nice guy :) Way better than the Sinclairs lol

Best, teacher, ever. MIE100 might be one of the hardest first year courses around, but it won't seem like it if Dr. Simmons is teaching it. He is very clear, takes time to make sure the majority of the class understands, and is funny as hell. He also does a lot of research with biomedical stuff, so talk to him if you think its interesting.

He is excellent at teaching.  Very practical, uses great examples (from previous exams) to clarify concepts.  Willing to help you if you are willing to learn.  Better prof than Leslie Sinclair (i went to both).  Most recommended prof for this course if still teaching
